README

Hmmm... 
So let's try and reduce the need to download and upload a php file while trying to fix a few issues. Sometimes a PHP file has to be tested in a specific environment and frequence upload and test takes lot of time. 
Similar to the wordpress editor which allows editing files and saving the changes.

This version is the editor and previewer. Please check the other version for editing existing files via browser editor and saving them directly on the server.

v9.8 Editor and Previewer : Let's Start